# ManyChat Prototype — Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
Interactive prototype of a ManyChat-style chat marketing & automation platform.
Built with React + TypeScript + Ant Design 5 + Styled Components.

## Tech Stack
- React 18 with TypeScript
- Vite for dev server
- Ant Design 5 (antd) as the component library
- Styled Components for custom styling
- React Router for navigation
- All code in TypeScript (.tsx / .ts files only)

## Design System Rules

### Use Ant Design As the Base
- Always use Ant Design components before creating custom ones
- Import from `antd` directly: `import { Button, Card, Table } from 'antd'`
- Import icons from `@ant-design/icons`
- Use Ant Design's ConfigProvider for theme overrides — never override antd CSS directly

### Styled Components Layer
- Use styled-components ONLY for layout, composition, and custom styling on top of Ant Design
- Name styled components with an `S` prefix: `SWrapper`, `SSidebar`, `SContent`
- Keep styled components in the same file as the React component
- Use the theme object from our theme.ts for all values

### Theme Tokens (Use These, Don't Hardcode)
```ts
colors:
  primary: '#6E3FF3'        // Purple — main brand
  primaryHover: '#5B2ED9'
  secondary: '#00B4D8'      // Cyan — accents
  background: '#F5F5F5'     // Light gray page bg
  surface: '#FFFFFF'         // Card/panel bg
  sidebar: '#1A1A2E'        // Dark sidebar
  sidebarHover: '#2A2A4A'
  text: '#1A1A2E'           // Primary text
  textSecondary: '#6B7280'  // Secondary text
  border: '#E5E7EB'
  success: '#10B981'
  warning: '#F59E0B'
  error: '#EF4444'

spacing:
  xs: 4px
  sm: 8px
  md: 16px
  lg: 24px
  xl: 32px
  xxl: 48px

borderRadius:
  sm: 6px
  md: 8px
  lg: 12px

breakpoints:
  mobile: 768px
  tablet: 1024px
  desktop: 1280px
